data.description: This adorable 4 bedroom home provides ample indoor and outdoor space! Updated and beautiful kitchen are perfect for cozy get-togethers! Take your pick of bedrooms - two on the main floor, or spread out with one upstairs another in the lower level. Upper and lower levels provide dedicated areas for downtime! Outside you'll be able to let the kids or furry family members run in the fenced in yard! Need to relax, cast a line in the Sauk River or snooze on the hammock and enjoy the cool breeze from the shady trees! Enjoy a firework display on Friday evenings in the summer from your backyard!
